## Phase-tagged storage (DbOnly terminal)

Operations **dispatch** persistence is **DbOnly terminal** (Phase 6). Follow Sedea rule **0** ÔÇö do not mix retired Hybrid / FsReadOnly contracts.

| Phase | Agent contract |
|-------|----------------|
| **DbOnly (terminal ÔÇö only supported)** | Dispatch CRUD via workspace DB + MCP; no epoch-folder discovery; no filesystem dispatch bundle IO |
| ~~Phase 0 / Hybrid / FsReadOnly~~ | **Retired** ÔÇö not supported |

**DbOnly-only:** there is no supported flag-off, kill-switch, or feature-flag path that restores filesystem dispatch bundles or Hybrid / FsReadOnly IO. Agents must treat DbOnly as the only live contract ÔÇö do not chase deleted storage-phase feature flags as overrides.

Plans and docs under `.sedea/operations/.../plans/` and `docs/` remain filesystem for now (out of Phase 6 scope).

